      <h1>Bakery Display Counter Price & Options India 2026</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span>📅 Updated: March 2026</span>
        <span>⏱️ 10 min read</span>
        <span>🇮🇳 India-focused pricing</span>
      </div>
